00:13:29.041 --> 00:13:31.542
At school,
I just lost interest.

00:13:32.834 --> 00:13:35.208
I took pleasure
in tormenting my teachers.

00:13:38.208 --> 00:13:40.941
At that time for example,
AT&amp;T was the stock

00:13:41.141 --> 00:13:43.675
that all teachers owned
for their retirement,

00:13:43.875 --> 00:13:47.508
and I decided that it would
drive my teachers a little crazy

00:13:47.708 --> 00:13:50.375
if I went and short the stock,
because when you go short a stock,

00:13:50.575 --> 00:13:53.125
you're betting
that it will go down.

00:13:53.325 --> 00:13:54.883
So I shorted
10 shares of AT&amp;T,

00:13:55.083 --> 00:13:56.966
and then brought
the confirmation to school

00:13:57.166 --> 00:13:59.375
and showed these teachers
I was shorting the stock.

00:14:00.458 --> 00:14:01.883
They found me
a big pain in the neck,

00:14:02.083 --> 00:14:04.166
but they did think I knew
a lot about stocks.

