Well, I thought
he was a prodigy...

00:40:57.041 --> 00:40:58.217
and I got a lot
of criticism.

00:40:58.417 --> 00:41:01.792
My wife said,
"Why are you paying such enormous respect

00:41:01.992 --> 00:41:04.750
"to that young man
with a crew cut

00:41:04.950 --> 00:41:07.062
who won't eat vegetables?"

