Warren:
He's ungodly smart.

00:41:09.375 --> 00:41:12.375
He's got a much broader
intellect than I do,

00:41:12.575 --> 00:41:14.800
and he's magnificent
at being able

00:41:15.000 --> 00:41:19.358
to condense important ideas
into just a very few words.

