01:00:40.241 --> 01:00:41.675
who didn't even know
about the deal.

01:00:41.875 --> 01:00:45.500
Salomon Brothers is under investigation
by the Treasury Department,

01:00:45.700 --> 01:00:48.834
the Federal Reserve, the SEC,
and the Justice Department.

01:00:49.034 --> 01:00:51.917
But more important than
the fate of the firm itself

01:00:52.117 --> 01:00:54.104
is the impact
their actions could have

01:00:54.304 --> 01:00:56.291
on the public trust
and on the credibility

01:00:56.491 --> 01:00:58.291
of the American
market worldwide.

