a little staggering."

01:01:23.834 --> 01:01:26.000
And I was hoping he would say,
"Well, don't worry, Warren.

01:01:26.200 --> 01:01:27.883
We'll give you
a few weeks to breathe."

01:01:28.083 --> 01:01:32.417
And he... he said to me,
"Prepare for any eventuality."

