But physically,
I'm pretty well depreciated.

01:24:31.700 --> 01:24:33.458
I'm getting down
to salvage value.

01:24:39.417 --> 01:24:41.217
But it really doesn't make
any difference at all.

01:24:41.417 --> 01:24:44.500
It doesn't interfere with my work.
