01:24:44.700 --> 01:24:46.041
It doesn't interfere
with my thinking.

01:24:46.241 --> 01:24:51.050
????

01:24:51.250 --> 01:24:55.166
I don't feel any diminution
in my enjoyment of life

01:24:55.366 --> 01:24:56.592
or enthusiasm
for life at all.

01:24:56.792 --> 01:24:59.917
In fact, in a sense,
the game that I'm in

01:25:00.117 --> 01:25:01.959
gets more interesting
all the time.

01:25:03.208 --> 01:25:06.500
It's a competitive game.
It's a big game,

01:25:06.700 --> 01:25:09.625
and I enjoyed
the game a lot.

